{# Global 'evpn' ... 'exit' configuration block -- experimental config
scheme only (proteus-bgp-evpn-experimental.yang's top-level `evpn`
container, passed in as `evpn`). The caller (render_evpn_global)
guarantees the container has content; in the "frr" output format this
block has no stock equivalent and is not rendered at all. #}
